liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: A bit of extra bounce, a bit of extra venom and Kohli fends the ball off the splice of the bat to Steve Smith at second slip, who takes a ripper catch high above his head. Lovely bowling from Starc, brilliant catch from Smith, horrible trouble for India!
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: OUT! KOHLI FENDS  ONE TO STEVE SMITH AT SLIP!

children.content: A bit of extra bounce, a bit of extra venom and Kohli fends the ball off the splice of the bat to Steve Smith at second slip, who takes a ripper catch high above his head.
Lovely bowling from Starc, brilliant catch from Smith, horrible trouble for India!

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Another Indian player has been Maxwelled! Pujara just left that, and watched as the ball skidded back in a touch off the seam and cannoned into off stump! He goes for 14 and India are in trouble now at 3-50!
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: BOWLED HIM! PUJARA GOES NOT OFFERING A SHOT!

children.content: Another Indian player has been Maxwelled!
Pujara just left that, and watched as the ball skidded back in a touch off the seam and cannoned into off stump!
He goes for 14 and India are in trouble now at 3-50!

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Well, Australia were in control at lunch, they're definitely in control now. Two quick wickets, both openers back in the sheds and Scott Boland with a brilliant first three overs in England. Still a long way to go, but that's a superb start from the Aussies with the ball.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: Tea: India 2-37 (Pujara 3, Kohli 4)

children.content: Well, Australia were in control at lunch, they're definitely in control now.
Two quick wickets, both openers back in the sheds and Scott Boland with a brilliant first three overs in England.
Still a long way to go, but that's a superb start from the Aussies with the ball.
